<doc f='include/SDL2/SDL_gamecontroller.h' l='163'>/**
 *  Open a game controller for use.
 *  The index passed as an argument refers to the N&apos;th game controller on the system.
 *  This index is not the value which will identify this controller in future
 *  controller events.  The joystick&apos;s instance id (::SDL_JoystickID) will be
 *  used there instead.
 *
 *  \return A controller identifier, or NULL if an error occurred.
 */</doc>
